                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Gland, mes délices, viens, dresse\nQui dans ma main se harnache\nSoudain d’opale et de lait."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Ce n’est que pour une douce",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Mais quoi ton ardeur se fâche…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ce n’est que pour une douce\nMais quoi ton ardeur se fâche…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Ton caprice, règle unique.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Les voici tout prêts, en selle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ton caprice, règle unique.\nLes voici tout prêts, en selle,"
